data.description: Welcome to your charming retreat located in the desirable Gilmore Farms, where modern comfort meets timeless appeal. Nestled within the acclaimed Gull Lake Schools district, this well-maintained haven promises a warm and inviting living experience. Step inside and immerse yourself in the spacious, sunlit open floor plan. The main level welcomes you with a spacious living room featuring newer flooring, a vaulted ceiling adorned with its added beam, and delightful pallet accent walls - the perfect spot to unwind after a long day. Prepare culinary delights in the kitchen, a haven for any chef, featuring an array of cabinets and ample counter space. Highlights include pristine white cabinetry, a vaulted ceiling, durable vinyl plank flooring, a stylish tile backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. Retreat to the primary bedroom, boasting comfort and convenience with its private bath and oversized walk-in closet. Venture downstairs to discover even more space to relax and entertain, including an inviting family room, two generously sized bedrooms, and a second full bath. Completing this level is the laundry area and additional storage space. Step outside to your own personal oasis, complete with an inviting deck and patio, enhanced by a charming pergola. The meticulously landscaped yard is complemented by underground sprinklers and a privacy fence. Backing onto the community park adds to its appeal. The neighborhood itself is unparalleled, featuring a pool, water feature park, big wheel track, pavilion with picnic tables, play yard, and a serene pond surrounded by picturesque walking trails - truly a community like no other in Richland. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and local attractions such as The Gilmore Car Museum and Gull Meadow Farms, this home offers the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and community. So why wait? Come experience the best of both worlds at Gilmore Farms - where every day feels like a getaway!
